<html><head><meta charset="UTF-8"><link rel="stylesheet" type="text/css" href="css/tips.css"></head><body><p><b>Navigate to a file</b></p><p>To quickly open a file, press <span class="shortcut">&shortcut:GotoFile;</span> (<span class="control">Navigate | File</span>) and start typing its name. Use the filter icon to only search among the selected file types:</p><p class="image"><img src="images/ij_tips_gotofile.png" alt="Go to file" style="border: 1px solid #55555;" /></p></body></html>